CargoWorld - Cargo Management for ATS and ETS2






***********************

QUICK START FOR WINDOWS

***********************



ATS

1. Copy the cargoworld_telemetry_x64.dll into "American Truck Simulator\bin\win_x64\plugins" (create this folder if needed)


ETS2

1. Copy the cargoworld_telemetry_x64.dll into "Euro Truck Simulator2\bin\win_x64\plugins" (create this folder if needed)



2. Run cargoworld.exe



****************************

PYTHON (WINDOWS, LINUX, OSX)

****************************



1. Check that Python3.5+ is installed along with PyQt5 (Graphviz recommended to display cargo graphs)

2. Run 'python cargoworld.py' in the cargoworld folder




****
HELP
****

1. Visit https://sites.google.com/site/storymodsite/cargoworld
2. visit https://forum.scssoft.com/viewtopic.php?f=34&t=246807






*********

UNINSTALL

*********



1. Remove cargoworld_telemetry_x64.dll from the simulator plugins directory

2. Delete this folder if you want








